.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: red, green, ivory, yellow, blue
There are 5 different nationalities: english, spanish, ukranian, norwegian, japanese
The people have 5 different hobbies: collecting, sudoku, video-games, singing, drawing
The people have 5 different jobs:  software-developer, coach, project-manager, security-guard, electrician
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: blues, house, r&b, metal, disco

1. the english is the person who likes red
2. the spanish is the fan of blues
3. the software-developer is the person who likes green
4. the ukranian is the coach
5. the person who likes green is to the right of the person who likes ivory
6. the person who's hobby is collecting is the fan of disco
7. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the person who likes yellow
8. the project-manager is in the middle
9. the norwegian is on the far left
10. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left or right of the fan of house
11. the person who's hobby is sudoku is to the left or right of the fan of metal
12. the person who's hobby is singing is the security-guard
13. the japanese is the person who's hobby is drawing
14. the norwegian is to the left or right of the person who likes blue

.:: Answer ::.
|		|       1	|	2	|	3 	|	4	|	5	|
| Nationality	|   norwegian	|    ukranian	|     english	|    spanish	|    japanese	|
| Color		|    yellow	|      blue	|      red	|     ivory	|     green	|
| Job	|     electrician	|      coach	|      project-manager	| security-guard	|     software-developer	|
| Hobby		|     sudoku	| chesterfield	|    olg-gold	| singing	|   parliament	|
| Music-Genre		|     house	|     metal	|     disco	|     blues	|     r&b	|
